{"tid":1266798,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【你講我多多都聽！】如果你好灰心，又搵唔到人傾下放下負，你快啲同我入黎!!","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:19.000Z","uid":82955,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa3deb5f0e6953b8c3e8d0c812c691c9579e321","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"我相信對大家黎講都係一樣，今晚又會係另一個好難過嘅夜晚。大家可能會面對住一種好強烈好灰暗嘅感覺，可能會好傷心好難受，可能會有好強既無力感。<br />\n<br />\n如果你已經好難受，我好希望你可以暫時離開Social media，離開新聞，好好咁抽離一下，比自己好好休息。唔使因為自己暫時去抖下而覺得內疚。放心比自己抖一陣，其他人會幫你守住你嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\n我好希望大家可以好好搵身邊嘅朋友，同佢地分享你自己嘅諗法。開心，唔開心，廢話，咩都可以放鬆咁傾一輪，比自己好好抖下。如果你真係好難受，而又諗唔到可以搵邊個傾訴。你唔介意，又信得過我地嘅話，可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入黎呢個group，我地唔會比你自己一個唔開心落去，你多多咁講，我地多多咁聽。</span></strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果你都想幫手做聆聽者，安慰下有需要嘅人，我都好歡迎你入黎，聽下其他人嘅心事。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">I really wish I could give them a hug before they did that.</span><br />\nLove is all around. They loved us. And we should show our love, too, especially to those unseen.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">TG Group Link:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LVj_CRVDUG30O_V_2TkG4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLVj_CRVDUG30O_V_2TkG4A&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo8Q0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=0a4411db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LVj_CRVDUG30O_V_2TkG4A</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZzjvCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZzjvCQ.jpg&h=0c275689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n如果你需要專業一啲嘅幫助，記得聯絡佢地：<br />\n<br />\n良心理政 HK Psychologists Concern<br />\n95475781 （9am-11pm）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2RnUXK9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RnUXK9&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo8Q0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=be81552b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2RnUXK9</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n多謝你睇到呢到，記得去關心身邊所有人，同時唔好比太大壓力自己。<br />\nSENT WITH MY BIGGEST HUGS.</span>"},{"pid":"8f8e9b47a2b7b0c1a983945c93dcdde3e91fcf57","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"推！大家唔好自己一個面對問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWe stand together as one!"},{"pid":"30386cfcda506f646ba5f5ea393fc00ea9ecac6b","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"eeb1b1be57d4612d4b7aadaafb048c26ddd92aeb","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a6b9121527bd59ea8db5843dfe20eec9b3d84348","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7dcbe109997ab3d09884bb9a8768f0f071c16808","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fc8805cb9e68dad5802a9ff7c950e66dc51eb7e3","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a51472c5918dea6af2d747da1574944ec5b17a32","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4c941a8357654bb00a9da0c2d00a10c47de0a2e4","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:05:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1965af057ec990529dc14b470270c9c93ea6f775","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"baad323d3870272b2ada378febac48dd15602492","tid":1266798,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid"